{"tid":1789900,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"‎[集中討論] ONEPIECE 海賊王 第966話 漫畫情報","createTime":"2019-12-19T15:12:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-26T04:18:11.000Z","uid":130563,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"b3cfc79996c3826920ceea87ffea06ba0e486df0","tid":1789900,"uid":130563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T15:12:51.000Z","msg":"標題：羅傑與白鬍子 <br />\n扉頁：戚風在髮廊被海軍抓住了（有3個新海兵出場） ​​<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zApo3ku.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzApo3ku.jpg&h=53d9cf94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n==============<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Dfa7Lj8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDfa7Lj8.jpg&h=0af81395&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;和傳聞一樣！很強！<br />\n賈巴：趁早阻止他們吧！雷利<br />\n雷利：就這樣做吧<br />\n羅傑：等一下！賈巴！雷利！你們受傷可就不好了！<br />\n雷利&amp;賈巴：你就是想打架而已吧<br />\n御田：有野獸的氣息<br />\n羅傑：你好啊！武士<br />\n<br />\n--------------------<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dbbVUfe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdbbVUfe.jpg&h=124d25f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n羅傑：神避<br />\n<br />\n--------------------<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6Huo26P.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6Huo26P.jpg&h=faea759d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n白鬍子：精神頭不錯啊 羅傑<br />\n羅傑：多少年沒見了！紐蓋特<br />\n<br />\n--------------------<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ec3k4WR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEc3k4WR.jpg&h=53f7941a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n御田：「（武器）沒碰上！」<br />\n<br />\n--------------------<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BvLGPYK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBvLGPYK.jpg&h=36707d1e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n羅傑：早在13年前&hellip;&hellip;我們終於抵達到達了無人成功到達的「記錄指針」的終點，「水先星島」（Road Star）<br />\n<br />\n--------------------<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ksmnzdv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKsmnzdv.jpg&h=6285e5b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n羅傑：刻著&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;的四塊紅石！在從前「世界政府」禁止解讀的「歷史正文」，本以為只是文化遺產，沒想到還是我們必需的地圖<br />\n政府禁止人們去「最後的島嶼」，只要到達那裡我們就是名副其實的世界第一海賊團了<br />\n<br />\n--------------------<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TdYAUdt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTdYAUdt.jpg&h=65efe4ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黑鬍子：那些傢伙是見習的？<br />\n馬爾科：是啊&hellip;&hellip;從以前就在了<br />\n雖然看起來不怎麼強&hellip;&hellip;但是態度上已經很獨立了<br />\n巴基：香克斯，那裡有個戴帽子的傢伙吧<br />\n香克斯：嗯<br />\n巴基：那傢伙，昨天和（之前？）的晚上好像都沒睡覺<br />\n好像從出生以來一次覺都沒睡過<br />\n香克斯：誒！？還有這種人嗎！？真好啊！<br />\n他不睡覺的話，不就等於比別人得多活一輩子嗎？（猜測大意）<br />\n巴基：說什麼傻話，那就只是個怪物吧（猜測大意）<br />\n<br />\n--------------------<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xE26gEp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxE26gEp.jpg&h=1f89da06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n御田日記<br />\n我作為海賊的第二幕，新的冒險開始了！<br />\n雖然小白吉也很了不起<br />\n但羅傑也深不可測！我運氣真好！<br />\n<br />\n--------------------<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Vm3M06d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVm3M06d.jpg&h=dcbaabee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n雷利：真讓人想起從前啊<br />\n<br />\n--------------------<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o3YAUdw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo3YAUdw.jpg&h=7b77ad79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n巴基：好厲害！黃金！船長！這個怎麼拿回去啊！<br />\n（看不見）<br />\n羅傑？：我沒有時間了<br />\n巴基：誒&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;！就算是碎片也好啊！（推測）<br />\n羅傑：這塊石頭聲音很「強」，很容易發現，上面說的是強大的「力量」吧？<br />\n御田：上面寫著名叫波塞冬的兵器<br />\n羅傑：這樣雕！「我來到此處，將此文引至盡頭」！<br />\n御田：這樣就好了吧？<br />\n羅傑：幹得好！御田！<br />\n御田日記：讓我見識一下吧，羅傑，你賭上生涯的大冒險的最終章！<br />\n<br />\n--------------------<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4TaLxdx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4TaLxdx.jpg&h=daf6163e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n白團：給我上啊&mdash;&mdash;！！<br />\n羅團：給我搶啊&mdash;&mdash;！！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TgV33kz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTgV33kz.jpg&h=1a3555b3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3607e893a78a72b253333dbd4438dc132157313f","tid":1789900,"uid":68191,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T15:21:56.000Z","msg":"御田識呢古代文字<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ca67f1f82ed30816737b7a757c47891aecbd53e","tid":1789900,"uid":212,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T15:22:13.000Z","msg":"進展得好快 差唔多要睇御田死了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBtw原來黑胡子真係瞓唔到覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1685704d1d094c65663f3d6c9749de62bdf2c932","tid":1789900,"uid":2203,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T15:22:31.000Z","msg":"主角篇真係好好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c792215413cec3d2f555084a71c082af3ea73be","tid":1789900,"uid":212,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"3607e893a78a72b253333dbd4438dc132157313f","tid":1789900,"uid":68191,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T15:21:56.000Z","msg":"御田識呢古代文字<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T15:22:53.000Z","msg":"好早已經講過光月家族識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4920858f516c5569506065947ab3b2648c777f93","tid":1789900,"uid":130563,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T15:23:28.000Z","msg":"13年前！？估唔到原來咁早之前就已經去咗一次記錄指針個終點...<br />\n仲以為係最近去完，先至會搵御田加入...<br />\n<br />\n冇人去過記錄指針個終點，呢一點都好奇怪，<br />\nLaugh Tale難去好合理，Road Star都難去！？<br />\n照計班四皇應該個個都去過，唔係點會個個都知道要儲紅石？"},{"pid":"7b7ce0527ee542027ba2c39b324ba2c358058059","tid":1789900,"uid":68191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6c792215413cec3d2f555084a71c082af3ea73be","tid":1789900,"uid":212,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"3607e893a78a72b253333dbd4438dc132157313f","tid":1789900,"uid":68191,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T15:21:56.000Z","msg":"御田識呢古代文字<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T15:22:53.000Z","msg":"好早已經講過光月家族識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T15:24:01.000Z","msg":"唔記得左<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d25993e834f2068c958e92f035ebc937d9ae1916","tid":1789900,"uid":130563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3607e893a78a72b253333dbd4438dc132157313f","tid":1789900,"uid":68191,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T15:21:56.000Z","msg":"御田識呢古代文字<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T15:24:26.000Z","msg":"歷史本文係佢嗰一族刻架！代代相傳文字嚟。"},{"pid":"9337e95dfe63e7edd9eba2c3ae9c8d8487897002","tid":1789900,"uid":130563,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"1ca67f1f82ed30816737b7a757c47891aecbd53e","tid":1789900,"uid":212,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T15:22:13.000Z","msg":"進展得好快 差唔多要睇御田死了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBtw原來黑胡子真係瞓唔到覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T15:25:06.000Z","